                "title": "Sarah Osten, The Mexican Revolution's Wake: The Making of a Political System, 1920\u20131929 (Cambridge and New York: Cambridge University Press, 2018), pp. xiii + 285, \u00a375.00, hb.",
                "year": 2019,
                "venue": "Journal of Latin American Studies",
                "citation_count": 0,
